channel.title: Adding teleports to a 317?
channel.description:
Hey im trying to add teleports to a 317 so i can get to that location and start setting up things like train, shop, skill, ect.. Can someone please tell me how to add teleports to the Emote buttons on the server?
I just looked at the tut section for a second time and i still didnt see any tutorials on adding teleports to the emote tab.
